Daylight;;1996;;PG-13;;Action,Adventure,Drama;;5.9;;Rob Cohen;;Sylvester Stallone,Amy Brenneman,Viggo Mortensen,Dan Hedaya,Jay O. Sanders,Karen Young,Claire Bloom,Vanessa Bell Calloway,Renoly Santiago,Colin Fox,Danielle Harris,Trina McGee,Marcello Thedford,Sage Stallone,Jo Anderson,Mark Rolston,Rosemary Forsyth,Luoyong Wang;;Trouble strikes when runaway robbers in a getaway car hit truck full of explosives in the tunnel connecting Manhattan and New Jersey. Survivors are left in a weakened tunnel blocked at both exits. As Kit Latura approaches the tunnel, he sees the impact and knows he gotta take action. With time running out, he enters the tunnel through a system of maintenance walkways. Can he get the survivors out before the tunnel fills up?;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0116040/